  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114920/extras/4e9bb100ac473c4054f23b3c1a26a265.avif?t=1680293158\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><br>In Deltatile you can swap 2 tiles based on the current position of the ball and the last position where a swap occured. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114920/extras/d4d91aed74c6df6afda4f74cfb0900e0.poster.avif?t=1680293158\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114920/extras/d4d91aed74c6df6afda4f74cfb0900e0.webm?t=1680293158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114920/extras/d4d91aed74c6df6afda4f74cfb0900e0.mp4?t=1680293158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Throughout 65 levels you will have to creatively use this mechanic to reach the goal.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114920/extras/ab1a88f37af1d34d7a754e27df6ae7ef.poster.avif?t=1680293158\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114920/extras/ab1a88f37af1d34d7a754e27df6ae7ef.webm?t=1680293158\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114920/extras/ab1a88f37af1d34d7a754e27df6ae7ef.mp4?t=1680293158\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114920/extras/5370fadbb09b5ecd91c878726e8ecae5.avif?t=1680293158\" width=616 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 65 levels<br></li><li> 6 worlds, each with unique challenges<br></li><li> Original Soundtrack</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Usability Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Full Screen/Windowed mode<br></li><li> Resolution settings<br></li><li> Music and SFX control with seperate sliders<br></li><li> Rebindable hotkeys<br></li><li> Various 3D related settings<br></li><li> Unlimited undo<br></li><li> Unlimited level skipping<br></li><li> No timer</li></ul>Mouse and Keyboard is required to play this game.",
